    jump.\nRecord\tLeft Shift\t\tToggle Shadow recording (Start/Stop).\nReplay \tR\t\t\tSummon
    and restart the Shadow's playback.\nSkill\t\tF\t\t\tTrigger your active Friend
    Skill.\nInteract\tE\t\t\tTrigger Interactive Components (eg. read, pulling levers)."
  startVisible: 1
